{
  "stem": "14867.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only Jews, but-- and I remember that, anytime we had a Jewish holiday, from-- from our estate, from-- from the farm, a truck carried [INAUDIBLE] poultry and dairy would come in and distribute to-- to Jews who were in need.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during the year, he would help a lot of people, regardless of religion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was really very known, and he was always anxious to help people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, he had a terrific influence on-- on us, certainly on me, because he always tried to show us that money's not very important.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's nothing to be proud of if you have a little bit more money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Any time I was in school and we wanted to go away, there was, like, an excursion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He would always say, make sure to take along one kid who cannot afford to go with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I want to go to the movies, instead of $1, let's say, he would say, here's $2.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Make sure to take someone along with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I will always remember that he would take a little coin and put it on the edge of the table and push it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, you see, I had money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I just pushed it and the money disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It fell off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So you have money today, but tomorrow you might not have it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So don't take-- don't get attached to the value of money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that I always remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in Wilia, which was-- it's a village 25 kilometers from Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we would spend our vacation in-- in the winter and the entire summer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were five children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So each of us had the permission to bring one friend.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
